snippet.title: Secrets of the Waves - v2.0 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/muzboz      Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/muzboz
Play "Secrets of the Waves", and discover the mysteries on of the ocean...
https://muzboz.itch.io/secretwaves

I made "Secrets of the Waves" for Global Game Jam 2017.

Sail across an ocean using a compass to search for the stone pillars in search for the lost treasure!
